            "text": "yusqawna min ra<u>h</u>iiqin makhtuum<strong>in</strong>"
        },
        {
            "id": "26",
            "text": "khit<u>aa</u>muhu miskun wafii <u>dzaa</u>lika falyatan<u>aa</u>fasi <strong>a</strong>lmutan<u>aa</u>fisuun<strong>a</strong>"
        },
