            "text": "fa<strong>a</strong>lyawma <strong>al</strong>la<u>dz</u>iina <u>aa</u>manuu mina <strong>a</strong>lkuff<u>aa</u>ri ya<u>dh</u>akuun<strong>a</strong>"
